CustomField.description: Represents the most accurate end office wirecenter CLLI8 as based on DPI and/or custom geospatial analysis of the address. Logic is to use DPI CLLI8 if it matches OGM, if not, use DPI lat/long and find corresponding end office CLLI8 that point falls within (leveraging BSA source end office wirecenter polygons). Defaults to NULL - Master_CLLI8 renames for list consistency MLR Header: CLLI8
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Unique identifier for wire center associated with the service address
CustomField.label: Wirecenter
